Barry Evans (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barry_Evans_(actor) 0 Barry Joseph Evans (18 June 1943 – 9 February 1997) was an English actor best known for his appearances in British sitcoms such as Doctor in the House and Mind Your Language.
